  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为工业物联网评论系统设计一个状态流转图。核心场景是：当TelemetryStream产生一条新评论时，它应该先进入待审核状态，经过PLC逻辑处理后再交给ActuatorController执行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "Pending",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以Pending状态内部需要包含PLC逻辑和等待审核两个子状态。那审核通过和拒绝分别流向哪里？另外删除操作是物理删除还是逻辑删除？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "AwaitingModeration",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Deleted"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "审核通过进入Approved状态，拒绝进入Rejected状态。删除是终态，所有状态都可以被删除，删除后回到TelemetryStream表示资源释放。Approved内部要有Visible和Edited的循环，Rejected需要记录拒绝原因。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Deleted",
        "Visible",
        "Edited",
        "Hidden",
        "WithReason"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画一版：Pending包含AwaitingModeration，Approved包含Visible和Edited的互转，Rejected包含Hidden和WithReason，WithReason要连回PLC逻辑。EdgeNode负责隐藏态的处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "AwaitingModeration",
        "Approved",
        "Visible",
        "Edited",
        "Rejected",
        "Hidden",
        "WithReason",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "有个问题，Pending内部的流向画反了。应该是PLC_Logic指向AwaitingModeration，然后AwaitingModeration再指向ActuatorController，不是反过来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "AwaitingModeration",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已修正，PLC_Logic → AwaitingModeration → ActuatorController。另外我在每个主状态右侧加了注释说明，比如Pending标注\"评论从待审核开始\"，这样可读性更好。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Deleted"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "注释内容再精确一点：Approved要强调可见且可编辑，Rejected强调隐藏且可附加原因，Deleted强调永久移除。还有，确认一下所有触发事件标签——创建、审批、拒绝、删除、更新、添加原因。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Create Comment",
        "Approve",
