      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部调整完毕。最终结构：TelemetryStream触发Create Comment到Pending，Pending可Approve/Reject/Delete，Approved可循环Edit，Rejected经EdgeNode处理Hidden状态后可Add Rejection Reason再回PLC逻辑，所有终态Delete返回TelemetryStream。",
      "elements_involved": [
